e of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> <small>(2022)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Blood_%26_Fire\" title=\"Blood &amp; Fire\">Blood &amp; Fire</a></i> <small>(TBA)</small></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Maps</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i> <small>(2012)</small></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403135148\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.210 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 731/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8472/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 18522/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 4955/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2305/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.130/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.44 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  192.846      1 -total\n 76.22%  146.986      1 Template:Infobox_Book\n 75.79%  146.160      1 Template:Infobox\n 15.00%   28.924      1 Template:For-multi\n 14.71%   28.375      1 Template:Hatnote\n  5.58%   10.752      1 Template:GRRM_works\n  5.19%   10.000      1 Template:Navbox\n  2.09%    4.032      1 Template:Navbar\n  1.45%    2.792      3 Template:Transclude\n  1.35%    2.611      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18141-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403135148 and revision id 318195\n -->\n",
